If	 you	 have	 been	 struck	 by	 some	 misfortune,	 so	 they	(the	 disbelievers)	too	 have	 been	 struck	
earlier	with	the	same	misfortune;	these	are	the	days	in	which	We	have	allotted	turns	to	people;	
and	so	that	Allah may	make	known	the	believers	and	may	bestow	martyrdom	to	some	of	you;	
and	Allah does	not	befriend	the	unjust
